<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="Mike provides handyman services throughout <%= config['serving_area'] %>" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= config['base_url'] %>/assets/img/header.png" />
  <script defer data-domain="mikethehandyman.services"></script>

  <!-- Favicon-->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/img/icon.png" />

  <!-- HTML Meta Tags -->
  <title>Mike the Handyman Services</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Mike provides handyman services throughout <%= config['serving_area'] %>">

  <!-- Facebook Meta Tags -->
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= config['base_url'] %>">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Mike the Handyman Services">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Mike provides handyman services throughout <%= config['serving_area'] %>">
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= config['base_url'] %>/assets/img/header.png">

  <!-- Twitter Meta Tags -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta property="twitter:domain" content="mikethehandyman.services">
  <meta property="twitter:url" content="<%= config['base_url'] %>">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Mike the Handyman Services">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Mike provides handyman services throughout <%= config['serving_area'] %>">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= config['base_url'] %>/assets/img/header.png">
  <!-- Meta Tags Generated via https://www.opengraph.xyz -->

  <!-- Google fonts-->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Black+Ops+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)-->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <!-- jQuery -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.3.1/dist/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <!-- nanogallery2 -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/nanogallery2@3/dist/css/nanogallery2.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/nanogallery2@3/dist/jquery.nanogallery2.min.js">
  </script>
</head>

<body id="page-top">
  <header class="d-flex flex-column-reverse flex-md-row container my-5 pt-5">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-5" style="align-content: center">
      <h1 class="mb-1 text-font-nyc text-size-64">
        <img src="./assets/img/logo.png" class="img-fluid rounded"
          style="height: 150px; width: 100%; object-fit: contain" alt="Mike the Handyman Services">
        <span class="visually-hidden">Mike the Handyman Services</span>
      </h1>

      <h2 class="text-font-black-ops text-size-32 text-accented text-center">
        <strong>Serving <%= config['serving_area'] %></strong>
      </h2>

      <hr style="width: 100px; text-align: center; margin: 1.5em auto;" />

      <%= render "contact" %>

    </div>
    <div class="d-none d-lg-flex col-lg-7 row g-2 mx-4" style="align-content: center">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <img src="./assets/img/shed.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" style="height: 600px; width: 100%; object-fit: cover" alt="Constructed shed complete with tin roof and siding" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="./assets/img/framing.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" style="width: 100%; height: 296px;  object-fit: cover;" alt="Framing of a new constuction" />
        <img src="./assets/img/tile.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mt-2" style="width: 100%; height: 296px; object-fit: cover;" alt="Bright, new tile completed this bathroom" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h3 id="faq" style="margin-top: 20px">
      FAQ
      <a class="text-decoration-none fs-5" href="#faq">ðŸ”—</a>
    </h3>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: What jobs can you do?</strong></p>
        <p>A: I have experience in general home maintenance and repair work, new home construction, general renovations,
          as well as many outdoors tasks such as brushcutting, wood cutting & splitting, snow removal, and landscaping.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: Do you take small jobs?</strong></p>
        <p>A: I&#39;m happy to work on small and odd jobs.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: Can you do free estimates?</strong></p>
        <p>A: Of course. Give me a <a href="tel:<%= config['phone'] %>">call</a>, <a href="sms:<%= config['phone'] %>">text</a>, or <a target="_blank" href="<%= config['facebook'] %>">message me on Facebook</a>.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: What is your Phone Number?</strong></p>
        <p>A: <%= config['phone'] %></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: What is your email?</strong></p>
        <p>A: <a href="mailto:<%= config['email'] %>"><%= config['email'] %></a></p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Q: Can you deliver large materials such as flooring, lumber, or stone?</strong></p>
        <p>A: It is preferable that you have the material delivered. However, I am happy to negotiate a delivery price using my truck and trailer.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
         <p><strong>Q: Do you have any earth moving equipment or tractors?</strong></p>
         <p>A: Yes, I have a tractor with a front-end loader and backhoe. It is appropriate for residential and rural jobs, as well as snow removal. If required, I also have experience with and can rent larger equipment such as Skid Steers, Excavators, etc.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h3 id="gallery" style="margin-top: 20px">
      Gallery
      <a class="text-decoration-none fs-5" href="#gallery">ðŸ”—</a>
    </h3>

    <div class="col-lg-12" data-nanogallery2='{"thumbnailWidth":   "auto", "thumbnailHeight":  400,  "thumbnailBorderVertical": 1, "thumbnailBorderHorizontal": 1, "viewerTools":     {
"topLeft":    "pageCounter",
"topRight":   "playPauseButton, zoomButton, fullscreenButton, closeButton"
},  "galleryDisplayMode": "moreButton", "galleryDisplayMoreStep": 8 }'>
      <%= render "image_gallery" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Call to Action-->
  <br />
  <section class="content-section my-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="mb-3 text-font-black-ops text-size-32 text-accented">Mike the Handyman Services</h1>
    <p><i>Serving <%= config['serving_area'] %></i></p>
    <%= render "contact", container_class: "w-100 max-width-500" %>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer-->
  <footer class="footer text-center mb-5">
    <div class="container px-4 px-lg-5">
      <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
        Copyright &copy; <span id="year">2025</span>
      </p>
      <script>
        document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
      </script>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-7qAoOXltbVP82dhxHAUje59V5r2YsVfBafyUDxEdApLPmcdhBPg1DKg1ERo0BZlK" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </script>
</body>
</html>